# NayePankh Foundation — Data Analytics Project

> **Internship Project | Domain: Data Analytics**
> Simulated end-to-end analytics pipeline for a non-profit foundation — from raw data generation to an interactive HTML report with dashboards, donor segmentation, impact scoring, and predictive forecasting.

